items.headline: Welcome to the Great Gatsby wiki.
items.desc: Welcome to the Great Gatsby wiki. We’re a collaborative community website about F. Scott Fitzgerald's novel The Great Gatsby that anyone can edit.  The Great Gatsby has been adapted numerous times, in various media. Gatsby has been filmed four times and is being filmed for the fifth time. Click the edit button at the top of any page to get started!

items.headline: The Great Gatsby Wiki
items.desc:
Ever heard of 'The Great Gatsby' before? This wiki was made for the new upcoming movie that comes out May 23, 2013 starring Leonardo DiCaprio, Carey Mulligan, and Toby Maguire. 

Jay Gatsby (DiCaprio), a rich millionaire, is obsessed with Daisy (Mulligan). Even though Daisy is married to Tom Buchanan (Joel Edgerton), they desire each other. What will happen throughout the streets of Jazz Age's New York? 

Come one, come all, to Everything Great-Gatsby! Come contribute to our wiki!
